{"tid":1953700,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Martha]Zack Snyder直播再次解釋《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》最具爭議的「Martha片段」","createTime":"2020-04-01T10:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T03:45:31.000Z","uid":249940,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8d88e8e455068ad1abf2af7c163a30a957460b","tid":1953700,"uid":249940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:22:47.000Z","msg":"3 月 25 日是《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》上映四周年的日子，查克決定透過 vero 直播與粉絲們一同重溫這部電影，並針對這部電影與粉絲分享他想補充的細節或想法。而查克在裡頭也針對片中著名的「瑪莎」片段解釋一番。<br />\n<br />\n「這其實是一個塑造角色的概念：蝙蝠俠因為丟失了原本謹守的道德信念，而變成了我們看到的這個樣子。」查導娓娓道來，「這整部電影的轉捩點就是當蝙蝠俠看到了超人的『人性脆弱面』，想起了初衷的那一刻。我想傳達的是『大家都是人類，某種程度上我們的人性是有共通點的』，即使僅僅是兩人的母親同名這一點也能點醒當下的蝙蝠俠『即使是擁有能力的外星人都是有母親的』，從而發覺超人也是有人性的，就這麼簡單。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=emb_title&amp;v=3FiInxv3f0o&amp;ebc=ANyPxKrJIvcidTpltuX-XMLd_iuN4t1aXv-Xnm_v2g_Vl-imo-p1yApNoU7mtOOTnvPtrusbPQYiBCkuC_Jxq1wbdFjgWynmAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Demb_title%26v%3D3FiInxv3f0o%26ebc%3DANyPxKrJIvcidTpltuX-XMLd_iuN4t1aXv-Xnm_v2g_Vl-imo-p1yApNoU7mtOOTnvPtrusbPQYiBCkuC_Jxq1wbdFjgWynmAQ&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=15ab3713\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=emb_title&amp;v=3FiInxv3f0o&amp;ebc=ANyPxKrJIvcidTpltuX-XMLd_iuN4t1aXv-Xnm_v2g_Vl-imo-p1yApNoU7mtOOTnvPtrusbPQYiBCkuC_Jxq1wbdFjgWynmAQ</a>"},{"pid":"f74388548b55c9dec60eb92aea5f22c31fc55644","tid":1953700,"uid":53769,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"成個怨婦咁 套戲都咁多年 捨得放口未"},{"pid":"cc677e8328a3c8631850cabf7cbb572baacc6af7","tid":1953700,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"What say that name ar"},{"pid":"41196955c469340dfbc3e16943b55eb58cf4a558","tid":1953700,"uid":249940,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f74388548b55c9dec60eb92aea5f22c31fc55644","tid":1953700,"uid":53769,"like":24,"dislike":4,"sco